# Tmux
## Download and Install
refer
[Tmux](https://tmux.github.io)
## Shortcuts
### Sessions
* :new _new session_
* s _list sessions_
* $ _name session_

### Windows 
* c _create window_
* w _list window_
* n _next window_
* p _previous window_
* f _find window_
* , _name window_
* & _kill window_

### Panes
* % _vertical split_
* " _horizontal split_
* o _swap panes_
* q _show pane number_
* x _kill pane_
* + _break pane into window_
* - _restore pane from window_
